author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Really that stream is already the most memorable ever :_ちょうちょ: :_きゅん: :_るんるん:

Wow... First, starting with a cover song, and later, direct at Makai world, but with more colored lights than her 3D debut. :_サイリウム碧: :_サイリウム紫: :_ハート:

Also, the most funny part were the games, the first one was the same squared alternatives as New Year's activity at Hololive's official channel. Next one was the buzzer game.
Special guests:
:_ちょうちょ: Oozora Subaru-san (Hololive 2nd Generation member),
:_ちょうちょ: Usada Pekora-san, Shirogane Noel-san, Shiranui Flare-san and Houshou Marine-san (Holofantasy members and Rushia-daitenshi's fellow partners),
:_ちょうちょ: Akai Haato-san (Hololive 1st Generation Member)
:_ちょうちょ: Murasaki Shion-chan (Hololive 2nd Generation member)
:_ちょうちょ: Tokino Sora-san (Hololive's Leader and founder member)

And the encore... Live Concert and the goodies... And an extra... Her New Live2D 3.0, presumably modeled also by Tou Ilie, who made a good job for Rushia and Yasuyuki-sensei.

And premiering "Iris", Original Song composed between Round Table and Rushia-daitenshi. :_ハート:
Also premiered as short version following next of this delivery.

Personally talking:
Really I knew about that, and really I loved everything... Too much time she didn't made a 3D Delivery like this, since 2019 November 30th. (Her 3D premiere), and I only watched as archive her 3D premiere; now I watched as Live 2 3D deliveries: this and the "3D at Home"/"Ouchi 3D" streamed at 2020 September 29th.
About her own song, really I loved it... It's like... Literally a Love Letter she sent to us... Maybe is taking the idea about starting 2020 September 6th stream, when returned her habit of kissing the audience and becoming more closer. Really I love her song than the mine I composed at June 2020 (I was thinking on that since I found her at May 2020 and discovering her beautiful vocal skills... I confess it... Also taking a little advantage of being the sucessor of my master since October 2019... But well... I can't tell sad things)
Definitively Rushia is the girlfriend which everyone single wants to meet... :_ハート: :_るんるん:
Happy Birthday, beautiful Necromancer :_るんるん: :_ちょうちょ: :_サイリウム碧: :_サイリウム紫:
